{"title":"中国，六月六日","authors":["陈绍伟"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，六月六日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈绍伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我朝思暮想的母亲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你离我的家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么遥远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又那么亲近。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个中国的公民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来迟了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十岁才走完这段路程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我来得正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶上庄严的时分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月六日下午三时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在人民大会堂前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到春潮簇拥母亲圣洁的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六届人大代表步入会场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们当中呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我尊敬的前辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的目光沉着、坚定；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国的开拓者呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎马生涯又走几程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有我同龄的战友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的脚步稳健、有力；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为建造共和国大厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人到中年，华发早生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有比我年轻的弟妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的笑意似蓓蕾初绽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为实现共同的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贡献超出他们的年龄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！他们是我们当中的一员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是万马军中的一个兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着十亿儿女的信念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着十亿儿女的深情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从天涯海角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北国山岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到一起呵走到一起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在母亲的身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个民族团结的大家庭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久久站在天安门广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我的心在倾听、倾听……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在倾听母亲的叮嘱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何止是三千多名代表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有正在攻关的教授，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有强悍的蒙古族牧民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有在葡萄园的维吾尔族姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有在法卡山哨所持枪的士兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有世居宝岛的高山族长者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我的儿子——小红领巾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的意愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇集在母亲的心脏——北京；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的权力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行使在这神圣的时分！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，六月六日下午三时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又将传遍山山岭岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们向着新的目标扬帆远航，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们迎着新的胜利挥动长缨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们会离开北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去开发南海油田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去征服原始森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去把宏图变成现实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去创造人间的奇景……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“六月六日下午三时”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的手表已对准北京时间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从这里出发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着母亲的重托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张又一张捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象彩霞一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点祖国的每一个早晨。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}